@AlexBillioux @AyameDinkler @Crimealytics Turns out, COVID unfortunately ended up being the big agenda for the year!

(@Lauren_Leist is ALMOST over this, Alex. Almost.)
@CEStephens @AyameDinkler @Crimealytics Not just a televised speech, but one that set out the agenda for the year…

@Crimealytics Well compare the CoVid data pattern year over year, then compare it to missing “ flu” season data. Same exact pattern! Same results regardless of masks,vaccines, lockdowns etc! No published Flu data! There are SO Many  ?????  And the truth will be unsettling to many.
@AyameDinkler @Crimealytics Thank you both for your advocacy and hard work to keep us informed and healthy and safe.

@Crimealytics It was the first day of the 2020 Legislative Session.  I recall vividly the Governor’s address to the joint session.  He announced that Louisiana had completed 15 tests at the state’s pubic health lab.
@AyameDinkler @Crimealytics Finding out an hour before a televised speech was … a lot.
